"list, the `#qgis <https://web.libera.chat/?channels=#qgis>`_ channel on IRC "
"or the `#qgis:matrix.org <https://matrix.to/#/#qgis:osgeo.org>`_ room!"
msgstr ""
"Pakalbėkite su mumis `qgis-community-team "
"<https://lists.osgeo.org/mailman/listinfo/qgis-community-team>`_ sąrašyne, "
"`#qgis <https://web.libera.chat/?channels=#qgis>`_ IRC kanale ar "
